<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +5</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> darkvision 60 ft.</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 2 (450 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Sight.</em></strong> The griffon has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The griffon makes two attacks: one with its beak and one with its claws.</p>

<p><strong><em>Beak.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 8 (1d8 + 4) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claws.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.</p>

